der rounds since 2017, a position now worth roughly $15 billion after compo=
unding at 54% per year.  </p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">He believes SpaceX,=
 coming public at under $2 trillion, will reach $10 trillion to $30 trillio=
n within 10 years and become the largest, most profitable company on the pl=
anet. </p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">People inside the company tell him he =
is lowballing it.  </p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">On Starlink alone, Baron =
projects 300 million subscribers and about $1 trillion in annual revenue wi=
thin a decade, making it worth around $14 trillion on its own.</p><p style=
=3D"margin:10px 0">Meanwhile I have never ever seen so much delusion around=
 an IPO in my life out there.  As usual I am unfaded and stick the the numb=
ers.  And yeah, Ron ALWAYS SANDBAGS.  </p><p></p></div></td></tr>
